🔐 5. File Permissions
🔹 Types
•	r → read
•	w → write
•	x → execute
🔹 Users
•	Owner
•	Group
•	Others
🔹 Number System
•	7 = rwx
•	6 = rw-
•	5 = r-x
•	4 = r--
chmod 755 file.txt
chmod +x file.sh
chmod 777 file.txt
chmod 600 file.txt
🔹 Ownership
chown user file.txt
chown user:group file.txt
🔹 Check Permissions
ls -l
